trans-unit.source: toUtf8() returns a UTF-8 encoded 8-bit string. UTF-8 is a superset of US-ASCII (ANSI X3.4-1986) that supports the entire Unicode character set through multibyte sequences.

trans-unit.source: QStringList and QByteArray are the only two non-primitive types that are supported directly by QDBusArgument because of their widespread usage in Qt applications.
trans-unit.target: QStringList和QByteArray是QDBusArgument直接支持的仅有的两个非基本类型，因为它们在Qt应用程序中的广泛使用。

trans-unit.source: QStringList inherits from QList<QString>. Like QList, QStringList is implicitly shared. It provides fast index-based access as well as fast insertions and removals. Passing string lists as value parameters is both fast and safe.
trans-unit.target: QStringList继承自QList < QString >。像QList一样，QStringList是隐式共享的。它提供了基于索引的快速访问以及快速的插入和删除。将字符串列表作为值参数传递既快速又安全。

trans-unit.source: QStringList provides both Java-style iterators and STL-style iterators. The Java-style const iterator is simply a type definition for QListIterator<QString>.
trans-unit.target: QStringList提供Java样式的迭代器和STL样式的迭代器。Java样式的const迭代器只是QListIterator < QString > 的类型定义。

trans-unit.source: QStringList provides both Java-style iterators and STL-style iterators. The Java-style non-const iterator is simply a type definition for QMutableListIterator<QString>.
trans-unit.target: QStringList提供Java样式的迭代器和STL样式的迭代器。Java风格的非const迭代器只是QMutableListIterator < QString > 的类型定义。

trans-unit.source: QStringView can also be used as the return value of a function. If you call a function returning QStringView, take extra care to not keep the QStringView around longer than the function promises to keep the referenced string data alive. If in doubt, obtain a strong reference to the data by calling toString() to convert the QStringView into a QString.
trans-unit.target: QStringView也可以用作函数的返回值。如果调用返回QStringView的函数，请格外小心，以使QStringView的保留时间不要长于该函数所承诺的保持引用的字符串数据存活的时间。如有疑问，请通过调用toString（）将QStringView转换为QString来获得对数据的强引用。

trans-unit.source: QStringView does not support mutable iterators, so this is the same as const_iterator.
trans-unit.target: QStringView不支持可变的迭代器，因此与const_iterator相同。

trans-unit.source: QStringView does not support mutable pointers, so this is the same as const_pointer.
trans-unit.target: QStringView不支持可变指针，因此与const_pointer相同。

trans-unit.source: QStringView does not support mutable references, so this is the same as const_reference.
trans-unit.target: QStringView不支持可变引用，因此与const_reference相同。

trans-unit.source: QStringView does not support mutable reverse iterators, so this is the same as const_reverse_iterator.
trans-unit.target: QStringView不支持可变的反向迭代器，因此与const_reverse_iterator相同。

trans-unit.source: QStringView is designed as an interface type; its main use-case is as a function parameter type. When QStringViews are used as automatic variables or data members, care must be taken to ensure that the referenced string data (for example, owned by a QString) outlives the QStringView on all code paths, lest the string view ends up referencing deleted data.
trans-unit.target: QStringView被设计为接口类型；它的主要用例是作为函数参数类型。当QStringViews用作自动变量或数据成员时，必须注意确保所引用的字符串数据（例如，由QString拥有）在所有代码路径上都超过QStringView，以免字符串视图最终引用已删除的数据。
